ZH: 我正在学习汉语。
EN: I am learning Chinese.

ZH: 汉语是世界上最流行的语言之一。
EN: Chinese is one of the most widely spoken languages in the world.

ZH: 我的汉语口语不够流利。
EN: My spoken Chinese is not fluent enough.

ZH: 你喜欢学习汉语吗？
EN: Do you enjoy learning Chinese?

ZH: 汉语的发音很复杂。
EN: Chinese pronunciation is very complex.

ZH: 在中国，人们都会说汉语。
EN: In China, everyone speaks Chinese.

ZH: 学习汉语对我来说很有挑战性。
EN: Learning Chinese is very challenging for me.

ZH: 我想要提高我的汉语水平。
EN: I want to improve my Chinese proficiency.

ZH: 我的朋友正在教我说汉语。
EN: My friend is teaching me Chinese.

ZH: 你可以帮助我学习汉语吗？
EN: Can you help me with learning Chinese?

ZH: 用彩色笔学习汉语有助于记忆生字。
EN: Using colored pens to study Chinese helps with memorizing characters.

ZH: 学习汉语的过程中，需要持之以恒。
EN: Perseverance is needed in the process of learning Chinese.

ZH: 我每天花30分钟学习汉语。
EN: I spend 30 minutes each day studying Chinese.

ZH: 你认为汉语比英语难学吗？
EN: Do you think Chinese is harder to learn than English?

ZH: 学习汉语让我感到充实。
EN: Learning Chinese makes me feel fulfilled.

ZH: 我在大学学习汉语。
EN: I am studying Chinese in university.

ZH: 汉语是一门古老而美丽的语言。
EN: Chinese is an ancient and beautiful language.

ZH: 我在网上找到了一个好的汉语学习资源。
EN: I found a good online Chinese learning resource.

ZH: 我想学会用汉语写信。
EN: I want to learn how to write letters in Chinese.

ZH: 汉语是中国的官方语言。
EN: Chinese is the official language of China.
